original_title: Paris By Night 90: Chân Dung Người Phụ Nữ Việt Nam
overview: Paris By Night 90: Chân Dung Người Phụ Nữ Việt Nam (English translation: The Portrait of a Vietnamese Woman) is a Paris By Night program produced by Thuy Nga that was filmed at the Terrace Theater at the Long Beach Convention and Entertainment Center on September 15, 2007 and September 16, 2007.
title: Paris By Night 90: Chân Dung Người Phụ Nữ Việt Nam
